-- Nigeria's forex reserves down 5.76 pct month-on-month to $37.8 bln
-- By Oludare Mayowa
-- Mon Mar 31, 2014 09:24AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, March 31 (Reuters) - Nigeria's foreign exchange reserves dropped 5.76 percent month-on-month to $37.80 billion as of March 28, the latest central bank data showed on Monday.

